at": "2017-04-22T08:23:36Z", "closed_at": "2017-04-22T08:23:36Z", "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR", "body_html": "<p>Hello, here is an example:</p>\n<pre><code>sums = torch.FloatTensor(3, 3, 4, 4)\nsums.uniform_()\n\nx = Variable(torch.FloatTensor(3,3,2,2).fill_(1))\nl = nn.Conv2d(3,3,2,bias=False)\nl.weight.data = sums[:,:,0::2,0::2]\no1= l(x)\n\nl.weight.data = sums[:,:,0::2,0::2].contiguous()\no2 = l(x)\n\nprint o1,o2\n</code></pre>\n<p><code>o1</code> will be different to <code>o2</code>.</p>", "body_text": "Hello, here is an example:\nsums = torch.FloatTensor(3, 3, 4, 4)\nsums.uniform_()\n\nx = Variable(torch.FloatTensor(3,3,2,2).fill_(1))\nl = nn.Conv2d(3,3,2,bias=False)\nl.weight.data = sums[:,:,0::2,0::2]\no1= l(x)\n\nl.weight.data = sums[:,:,0::2,0::2].contiguous()\no2 = l(x)\n\nprint o1,o2\n\no1 will be different to o2.", "body": "Hello, here is an example: \r\n\r\n```\r\nsums = torch.FloatTensor(3, 3, 4, 4)\r\nsums.uniform_()\r\n\r\nx = Variable(torch.FloatTensor(3,3,2,2).fill_(1))\r\nl = nn.Conv2d(3,3,2,bias=False)\r\nl.weight.data = sums[:,:,0::2,0::2]\r\no1= l(x)\r\n\r\nl.weight.data = sums[:,:,0::2,0::2].contiguous()\r\no2 = l(x)\r\n\r\nprint o1,o2\r\n```\r\n\r\n`o1` will be different to `o2`. "}